data.description: Spacious well maintained home in Yukon's Chisholm Crossing! This beauty has an open concept split floorplan with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a half bath located in the upstairs BONUS ROOM! The large bonus room can be configured to be a theatre room, game room, office, or even an optional 5th Bedroom with the large closet. Kitchen features granite countertops, S/S appliances, and large island with breakfast bar. Master suite features a large closet, oversized walk-in shower, and jetted tub! This 3 car garage features epoxied floors and a STORM SHELTER! The large covered and screened-in back porch is perfect for relaxing evenings or entertaining! You don't want to miss out on this one!
